properties.Name: PriceListType
properties.Description:
A classification of Price Schedules based upon common characteristics, attributes, functions or marketing objectives.

Ex:
-  Consumer Price Schedule
-  Government Price Schedule
-  Corporate Price Schedule
-  Introductory Price Schedule
-  Standard Price Schedule
-  Channel Price Schedule
-  Wholesale Price Schedule
-  Employee Price Schedule
-  Promotional Price Schedule
-  Seasonal Price Schedule
-  Geographic Price Schedule
-  Domestic Price Schedule
-  International Price Schedule

Columns.Name: PriceListTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Price List Type.

Columns.Name: PriceListTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Price List Type.

Columns.Name: PriceListTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Price List Type.

Columns.Name: PriceListForPartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: PriceListTypeFactor
Columns.Description: Sale Multiple - Indicates whether the given Unit price is for 1 or Multiple Items
